name: MyMovies
0:
”Alexa, ask my movies what movie should I watch today?”
”Alexa, open my movies”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my movies
des: Are you and your friends constantly wasting time and energy to find a movie to watch? Never fear for this app is here! This app will randomly select a movie for you and your friends so to minimize the time spent deciding on a movie that everyone can agree upon. Now you all can kick back and enjoy a movie.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
